data.title: About SINOPHARM WEIQIDA PHARMACEUTICAL CO. LTD.
data.meta_description: Sinopharm Weiqida Pharmaceutical Co Ltd is a comprehensive pharmaceutical manufacturer, invested and held by China National Pharmaceutical Group Corp, locating in Datong, which is a historic and cultural city and the energy base famous with coal.
data.text: Sinopharm Weiqida Pharmaceutical Co Ltd is a comprehensive pharmaceutical manufacturer, invested and held by China National Pharmaceutical Group Corp, locating in Datong, which is a historic and cultural city and the energy base famous with coal. We have production chains of Cephalosporin, Penicillin and Potassium Clavulanate products starting from Intermediates, APIs until Formulations.
